{"type": "article", "id": 2528, "title": "新 iPhone 保护套", "description": "", "date": "2014-09-24T08:23:19Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 5, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605232551P1bv9G8fITwVEFgC.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\tiPhone 6 和 iPhone 6 Plus 正式开售后前 3 天的销量超过了 1000 万部，各配件厂商也马上开始积极筹备新品的推出，英国配件品牌 Hard Graft 日前就及时推出了两款新 iPhone 的全新保护套，采用了招牌式的上等皮革以及意大利羊毛面料组合而成，安全密实的设计加上优质的材质能够为手机提供最好的防护，外部额外设计的口袋亦可以放置纸币、信用卡等随身小物。售价 85-89 英镑不等，<a href=\"http://www.hardgraft.com/collections/phone-cases/iphone6plus\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052325489svNLc0OZfArgUCP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5578125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232549AYaWhtjPNbCcmz5L.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5578125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232549Lwkj3AfmGlvJBF8M.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5578125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232549nW93fsSvPeBqKIZw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5578125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232550cgETl4R608dANaBW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5578125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}